	* doc/texinfo.tex (\documentlanguagetrywithoutunderscore): new macro,
	to try txi-de.tex if @documentlanguage de_DE.
	(\documentlanguage): call it.

	* lang.c (default_country_for_lang): just return country code, not
	whole locale string.

