2004-08-19  Stepan Kasal  <kasal@ucw.cz>

	* doc/texinfo.tex (\scanmacro): Make backslash active, not other,
	  as this is the default when processing texinfo files.
	  Otherwise, a \ inside @copying will eventually print as ``.

