	(\indexdummiesnofonts): call it.
	This is to semi-support macro calls in the arg to @deffn.
	Report from: Akim Demaille <akim@epita.fr>, 20 Apr 2004 17:48:28 +0200.

2004-04-21  Karl Berry  <karl@gnu.org>

