	* doc/texinfo.tex (\Orb): define if undefined.
	Report from Laurent Siebenmann.

	* util/dir-example: diff updates.

2004-04-13  Karl Berry  <karl@gnu.org>

	* doc/texinfo.tex: remove trailing blanks.  suggestion from Jim.

