	* makeinfo/macro.c (cm_alias): do not expand when calling
	get_until_in_line, since xml/docbook expansion is empty.
	Report from: Richard Kreuter <kreuter@anduril.rutgers.edu>,
	17 Sep 2003 17:59:58 -0400.

